metadata.name: Last photo of DOGE
metadata.description: Elon Musk and Dogecoin are like two peas in a pod. With their shared love of memes and off-the-wall ideas, they make an unlikely but hilarious duo. Whether they're launching a car into space or barking at each other on Twitter, they're always up for a good time. Who knows where their friendship will take them next? All we know is that it'll be a wild ride.
